'''开放宝市'''（{{lang-en|OpenBazaar}}）是一个[[去中心化|去中心化]]的[[电商|电商]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usv.com/blog/introducing-ob1|title=Introducing OB1|date=2015-06-11|website=Union Square Ventures|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-11|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216200001/http://www.usv.com/blog/introducing-ob1|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2016/03/16/openbazaar-silk-road-dark-web-drugs-ebay/#5814f3e76604|title=OpenBazaar Is Not The Next Silk Road -- It's An Anarchist eBay On Acid|date=2016-03-16|website=forbes|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2017-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217150709/http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2016/03/16/openbazaar-silk-road-dark-web-drugs-ebay/#5814f3e76604|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mt.sohu.com/20150722/n417293114.shtml|title=去中心化市场OpenBazaar将于2015年感恩节正式发布|date=2015-07-22|website=搜狐|5=|accessdate=2017-02-16|archive-date=2017-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218063243/http://mt.sohu.com/20150722/n417293114.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nigeriatoday.ng/2017/02/openbazaar-integrates-tor-the-platforms-most-requested-feature/|title=Openbazaar Integrates Tor – The Platform’s Most Requested Feature|date=2017-02-15|website=nigeriatoday|language=en|access-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217143223/https://www.nigeriatoday.ng/2017/02/openbazaar-integrates-tor-the-platforms-most-requested-feature/|archive-date=2017-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>她的用户使用多种与[[比特币|比特币]]类似的[[加密|加密]][[互联网|互联网]][[货币|货币]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.financemagnates.com/cryptocurrency/exchange/bitcoin-marketplace-openbazaar-now-accepts-a-variety-of-cryptocurrencies/|title=Bitcoin Marketplace OpenBazaar Now Accepts a Variety of Cryptocurrencies|date=2016-12-22|website=Finance Magnates|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-17|archive-date=2017-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217142756/http://www.financemagnates.com/cryptocurrency/exchange/bitcoin-marketplace-openbazaar-now-accepts-a-variety-of-cryptocurrencies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其灵感来自一个匿名组织的DarkMarket项目。

与依赖中央服务器交换数据的商业电商不同，开放宝市的服务器存在于用户们的[[對等網路|对等网络]]中，无任何监管中心，无任何手续费用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://money.163.com/15/0624/08/ASS2K3JD00253G87.html|title=这家公司可能是美国最危险的科技创业公司_网易财经|accessdate=2017-06-05|last=网易|work=money.163.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627161143/http://money.163.com/15/0624/08/ASS2K3JD00253G87.html|archive-date=2015-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他们的口号是“买卖自由/Buy and Sell Freely”。

